jk1665702673875.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sjk1665702673875.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sjk1665702673875.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sjk1665702673875\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the OCX messages that are directed to the Transcript Window.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"sjk1665702673875__topic_d145313e1_d145314e1_d145315e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sjk1665702673875__p_d145316e1_d145317e1_d145318e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">OcxTrace</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageCode</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sjk1665702673875__section_p2q_zpp_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d329829e65\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sjk1665702673875__p_d145322e1_d145323e1_d145324e1\">Allowed values are integers representing the sum of\n        message codes shown in the following table.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3198ab1b5b3b5_w3199ab1b5b3_w3200ab1b5_w3201ab1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Codes for selecting OCX messages</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3198ab1b5b3b5_w3199ab1b5b3_w3200ab1b5_w3201ab1__entry__1\">Code</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3198ab1b5b3b5_w3199ab1b5b3_w3200ab1b5_w3201ab1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3198ab1b5b3b5_w3199ab1b5b3_w3200ab1b5_w3201ab1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3198ab1b5b3b5_w3199ab1b5b3_w3200ab1b5_w3201ab1__entry__2\">No messages logged</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3198ab1b5b3b5_w3199ab1b5b3_w3200ab1b5_w3201ab1__entry__1\">1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3198ab1b5b3b5_w3199ab1b5b3_w3200ab1b5_w3201ab1__entry__2\">Log error messages (default)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3198ab1b5b3b5_w3199ab1b5b3_w3200ab1b5_w3201ab1__entry__1\">2</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3198ab1b5b3b5_w3199ab1b5b3_w3200ab1b5_w3201ab1__entry__2\">Log warning messages</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3198ab1b5b3b5_w3199ab1b5b3_w3200ab1b5_w3201ab1__entry__1\">4</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3198ab1b5b3b5_w3199ab1b5b3_w3200ab1b5_w3201ab1__entry__2\">Log information messages</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sjk1665702673875__table_w3202ab1b5b3b7_w3203ab1b5b3_w3204ab1b5_w3205ab1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"exp1665702673803.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exp1665702673803.html\" title=\"The [ocx] section of the initialization file is used to specify information about the environment in which OCXs run.\">[ocx]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sjk1665702673875__section_pnr_hqp_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d329829e175\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">For example, setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">OcxTrace</span> to <code class=\"ph codeph\">6</code> results in all\n        warning and information messages being logged.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532009\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532009\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "OcxTrace Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the OCX messages that are directed to the Transcript Window. OcxTrace = MessageCode Arguments Allowed values are integers representing the sum of message codes shown in the following table. Table 1. Codes for selecting OCX messages Code Description 0 No messages logged 1 Log error messages (default) 2 Log warning messages 4 Log information messages Default value 1 File section [ocx] Description For example, setting OcxTrace to 6 results in all warning and information messages being logged. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}